{"type": "article", "id": 11716, "title": "自助香水调配站", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-07T12:15:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115243BwUWHIG1pkRsCcKt.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t昨天我们介绍了英国皇家艺术学院 Jakub Pollág 的毕业作品，今天我们再来看两组毕业作品。Kyugum Hwang 制作了一个“自助香水调配站”，她设计了三个同心圆环，圆心固定在可旋转面板上。为了解决我们常常闻多了分不清楚味道的问题，她用不同的形状和颜色来区分香水的前调，中部和基调，使味道能够被更加直观地辨别，如果香水调配越来越自助化，相信这样的“自助站”将会派上不小的用场呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135804lx13LYRkQXjgJ697.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135806qpnKzQYb0EvOhr3S.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135807VFtqf7YRaDekNuGo.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135807F6WCgObjeYXExVnH.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135807XpcgyWUMSV05FTvB.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135808vmrd7aqz5IN9A2Mt.jpg\" width=\"784\" height=\"560\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}